<p rend="chapter">Puttakaṇḍa</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="281"><hi rend="paranum">281</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Abhijātaṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0168" /> anujātaṃ, puttamicchanti paṇḍitā;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Avajātaṃ na icchanti, yo hoti kulagandhano.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="282"><hi rend="paranum">282</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Pañcaṭṭhānāni <pb ed="M" n="0.0170" /> sampassaṃ, puttamicchanti paṇḍitā;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Bhato vā no bharissati, kiccaṃ vā no karissati.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="283"><hi rend="paranum">283</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Kulavaṃso ciraṃ tiṭṭhe, dāyajjaṃ paṭipajjati;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Atha vā pana petānaṃ, dakkhinaṃ anupadassati.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="284"><hi rend="paranum">284</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Bahuputte <pb ed="M" n="0.0171" /> pitā eko, avassaṃ poseti sadā;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Bahuputtā na sakkonti, posetuṃ pitarekakaṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="285"><hi rend="paranum">285</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Puttaṃ vā bhātaraṃ duṭṭhu, anusāseyya no jahe;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Kinnu chejjaṃ karaṃ pādaṃ, littaṃ asucinā siyā.</p>
